  "text": "The contamination of soil and water by industrial residues presents a huge threat to the environment due to their large wastewater output. In this context, the activity from food, cellulose, pharmaceutical and textile industries releases a myriad of pollutants, the highly stable structures of which may further hinder environmental remediation [CITATION_1] .",
